content.text:
I'm Claude Code, ready to help you explore and analyze your codebase! I'm in read-only mode, so I can search, navigate, and examine your code, but I won't be able to modify any files.

I'm equipped to:
- Search files using glob patterns (fast file matching)
- Search code content with powerful regex patterns
- Read and analyze specific files
- Run read-only commands to understand your project structure

What would you like me to help you explore in your codebase?
